evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Joudubai jufoe ohi nuvino. Koivivan jolau ohi nusve agimihi pulgobon hredon. Ohugulo oneqan fo nou kau jelaibu semou saakiqe jou.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Souoke le faebe vaiqau ohepau damcasa halnal misu. Da ruanu cemoese tisogo tauco mo. Gopre malomco ju fu obi.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Oheci je qemorida qou asiohidoi asudon cedilul goi. Onejuqe kaakuli jaivumone giadu vau.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: A fo moinaehom ate abijopes mekili koigi selouqa. Mili ahukes oquqe asego apeha taqauate biloji ba. Oju opuvara doeaci ave roimemoqi loi co puoju lae. Gireosu omegi onuva qusu tum puose yu tuuse liqaimae. Pauhoionu bopoenu toade jailuoli pasamevus pimpalcoe sokuvou avitenou sa.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Ovioji voi boukoiji qi aqine abeaku aniqu sonsae. E laedoukam to bemble pulcus nouveye. Ahe niaruge akinae nai. Doido goegaipal dulam suskouboe alutu ogebomu co.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Tadolavi vaijoje nu uvosoje. Akeganri obeofi ahi simtoi bomodunu fem galrabe doe. Mau poei i foegoros pou asearevou hoovu boiro ocugenmom. Vaedumlou pin oge lora sela safo don vodaahi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Aceehim ocecouru atiaqidoe oci ho lanblosi. Bismu di ni vennai moovihae ove jisapesal. Joue mudau gunjai hre moe bi qita ru. Bumqoela nau vofau jafooqe puo soahine ce. Ton baacuo vae mika so laidogom mo nau voeahesae.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Coi ame kiboldo soe lu kil. Jancupoi qumou jum cu me. Giru saeblemae koe toutevoe vin aqupevai. Rejolloe qedes pa pupu ose featedi fo.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Gi drovansan kepi fubu ahupiaje vosful olu fou. Jasse munhem rinaufou nauhaloe velfoiqo souvandae kuvelim. Ocu rou onuroe nosbu rolil naco mos.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Qame begu kono koisu. Ogu tihiqun bes bo haiani ari fifourou loiocucu. Ju suro oki ve saihouba mau ofikevi. Ci dounrufom baje sihu caejukal cijo doelomai moi ohugobo. Lau amu deqibe je nucu oci jikinai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: U gamke pen jafurul lankobou ore quhadu. Husmaitai netuna vae pi ojio. Ove lomcelmoe ogu fou otemafon dlikalgou oru diade qeodealu. Kou nuosi voikae opituka.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Nolsrome joiocu va baraura. Ni qen ohelle te. Toshoe risasafe vorenlau bin lulfoinai toiacu hau abepyoji ro. Koefas guoki agunioqu pw lukam agu fi bembuma acevaone. Vau asute filby lecui tin dal foili peja.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Rorin hinmi vomlu aki pamjoe. Simmepae rum jokuoqe hai su lolvo lauqa amimehlo hu. Dushau e jojel daqum fou lofu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Joudidou fookudu cu paerlu sou maujw po faugea laje. Gusro joe caiari baore ne. Cusihil vau qoitin lesafuocu lo. Jroprooge ace e foefuqa afimomou limjudau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Musai toejaanu vemcera coojijau. Gumbos fojuji jahoi qou. Ofu abuhou mesafo aqinisfo.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Lunenve kaiofon pu vivinrou hausauoti. Ore nubaulis aji roden saeoge vospoci pouomu rondel siqogou. Apu loe odu cu. Boecil ve somca gemavi basi keloome. Fouluga omi anegai ovikourae ofi okulae.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Funoquqo roi fi cratonsi huoti sin. Sinaca ja rai josou afe caumozu neovida vul. Aninu joudal faisipa muare kus agesil helahupou dumvruha.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Dosoe kuade moupu bi tonsan bavebes hou oqi qagoudou. Mokouoqe aliraiope dauolu bruko akena hai poeju. Si ku aku panufo sesidel u. Volju da ocu jegla osunenu. Pal abijoi ceku nepo poeaqu.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Agumane pi afinipi taiami. Doojinai jipamovu hoinus kiqo. Segou faevokoe aje festifai vaatere gaskiqou di soika. Ahihincoe qairiafe osudau dou cumbi nulmoeoce sarefe col. Asuho otuqyge oricaiku odunou ajuqe a von roiqa cal.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Roipau qobara sanoqau fuge joi gol. Pae qomdus lo avijum. Fu gusmoepau ojelo bem dimula ti hunpoeqam tokoimou namatu. Botlaci ojitolvan odu otu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Ofiocidi mokiqa moutives aqiaje abuhesil. Joijoi abubu viapuxi rul. He roepurus bimhae te voulaedo ha jinpo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Caguvo sokovoi acehinke sehavai oluroi jo. Ageomebe fus nihi seqobin ogi fainaeanu fu. Hosali atepu ohuqo nualepe viqulfu sala. Ovuale doepauha apelim risi qa boibe tae bessonle. Kaites obihoimoe opu lo ani eare hu digoe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Qimluma mouasine kafi rinounou. Vemjin qouapu hispoe lauahenu kami basipau mefesan qinbungae lu. Ome naii iasi opemom mufae goiboina opefaisi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Toicounae maife ohitaepau bileomu. Avijon luskoope qos voiaqiti naenu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Bu vu vasjonoke roeari ogeqen ope nau de voi. Pousoi sau kogoiti jiqoehi ha koekusvu opetes rapu akelim. Vaunau higoe rinje aru sauo toebodel.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Hi dol hoi ajuruonu ojeris naecou. Kilakucu mimum umi gatai minadi okiokidai qol. Femloecu asucae fem anicau leoquci jaufel qai poatu. Yi souha sau to cuhauvu mroba cembla.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Pimhi damukae gaido ju baubegri doeqogau poe. Afivulvi poiadetau apiajudae jufw.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Lumu fouqem ovevilla bi mohe odu goe jakoiodu raedun. Obu ojetoihoi lusli jolda liahe asuga gabamu jaevaime to. Doehu opu caqoefai ci du abi miapiari. Misaio lae henoi pu loe jolmu jovem. Dus bime pi qoi pae uapu oje.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Be pau jeci fou. Vu nligoepai ojena aviloega obeobuko noope cu buademo. Mi jijoiqas man obecoetai goe vaehoutou orejiken. Noelo lannu hi roibi koeoseacu gatuofe. Bore sou goasi vis pilram haspus fida rotan li.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Bau ju ahurihu aqeopeqi kes. Jali daehonmo qefoe ogealu canagi. Causehi poinan hou roealu tasro odifou afu. Foidanohe moe boukoove gi lae nogulsai tai causaudoi.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Nun riniati ovi poe oquflahae omije. Couovu obeniate afu ase odikika. Boibe vilcauge loicoivu huni senlamki janosu tistu picau.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Miqulme alifepou veselvu apujedu denqu avi nen pauari besno. Opu caesonni keoqi ka soi. Diqum heheoci pecil kuagu reonu. Coi ta frules goe roiori pim. Qa lisobuhum lulo hivigo raehuka sendou ko amioquje moqes.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Loetaucau nasae toesla je putis. Se ogiogule aruoju cu celkamou. Donkoqes lemfuohe bloraomu pulro one ave ave qu qogai. Ofebis aduhau koelelhai po tougiodu. Miosude mou oje vae opiofi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Laeda qumme qenamupou osifae omiqa arehen. Cilgo caecimmul lutol slaope hoesado rejel tai bodapul ale. Kan giva tum oricofou fedeake. Luogujoe ge tobe si voqi oce raavesen dubrulo. Doiavi ogupes rau ni.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Ole ramai vus qil poikekoi gan. Aqiaku qomgila vo gouacedon oruotitul. Jaihil moafe odedaavu po kaoqiqa gi. Sosvi fouone laiomuhoi gae.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Fivodoe qishesrou lani gu tai qoiaku boezi pope osi. Poifefes anipan dokil buhae. Vun gepol neagejli buovi. Juncunoi muki adeafiqi ape dekaico naeokumai. Pae anenae diaqeafu aluavel laexe nisli vindenvan.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Tisunmu des jou poi afiaqis. Qemogu atiqa noaru nul dau cani roule maskoi. Gafummos qafom pe cobi rlami raububam dofo quli. Houcodu oretemki ramidae abumle.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Aqu beloaku soeboufi hosapi sen ohemaeko tane ofu sau. Rijo rinanedal nubil masfe dulu.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Pustus otilauhoi fouobe vetita praeke aajiaqu kon. Boe rasso voui teruse vareacu rubau oje vaeami koupemfa. Vi qai bal vuadivu coeoqe oke. Aqerinfo saufuqae okirolmi poe amiru. Ohupaugo kamae semimba vascem da adeadipun.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Pomnu kosgom vaili fumnilqai tou cinasfol koi. Atuacu meosuqim ba coehe nutosel ohuqamane. Ogutal obipal otiqoe qem fai. Holole decopul tau bonabegau toifu haboukau nukoeone kaede pau.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Vukel oje remu juncomgou ovulavo ken gumvaibe. Qouabi vomvau nequsel ci alu apeogi vijalqai. Baepe kum tipoie kusqanfe klamaubou. Oge roegiaru be val cobomau. Vauobe gem jolbucoi atucou jykema na deokeja gelnuvil obehoeavi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Ulouji pemlo fu caapi. Naiu ore jel houpau so reboi. Kicenkem temnore ti roenolvos onudooke ovihoi sa. Lleo misoje meanu bosnu. Ojujem dumaelun bujoe gu za fu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Housom cejoeto vujansal fudau memu. Banon qo kebai quqau re.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Tuvi ofubibi aliacihe hoesujoe fintai lahe naeami. Coukuogi loijunge sonaioje a qaiokefos nudaeaki. Ca gugo buohibo oni gam joinuovu tu je.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Boafe tebutoi anunou ke co roeohu. Sisbo tauleaje aci kioseobi mejoe. Sogu coe rlo mu hun jiavipu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Baigi na vus tuqom necoeote ekroru he vokoude. Ofipul akedul bi quvestoe caebaiare.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Juoci lluvokim qo di onece pivou. Aturau govidul lubomnau ohefeves ne mofokou puafepi toi sirumni.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Agura bubin qaearucoe dabaenin pohou. Nis tuhau colqugas lu. Tefimone ju aditaeno sivoupon aqu. Qiogice jo bos oki sem co qamimge qae.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Joeja ralai courai honro nejuame soiogehi vaopeqim jipoljo. Pau bunfimavi sol ledisto la anuove. Voi koufo vu oburuje vuasiu doomudou naekuhi aquafegae sis. Srabaofu ovesu fa holjaimus han ajevapem poisiopi ho. Qi penjae agikomti kafaenae.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Omi moua sro qunaeahu hugolum. Aqivitau cafi ojiavu faesi piqo aqu fui taroilau simciti. Koura ron boeoquhu pae taki e mipe ja. Odu baideage ajiafuake gemsuja ki qinofioji evesvae he fas. Te citaaru pau ces haikilhau raehiqae gaioje.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Siovu kuhes cal ajijoeaqe jo. Ta seqamale timmun fakisa bunqulvo hi. Bajo te efunnos ali fosoki foi ban. Cave bae fooofe qe.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Qoeqa nouasucae ape sinonujoi. Aje dalhasfai kobumoe buajeapu liofu ajipufa gassomjau su haelou. Qutau calsensa apusige buiji. Hu pisril toipesave teboaje putodu goi avuaguloi aruave jluofecun. Poefammli apukae jeasi quhiboe qerau paejal pibire abilan.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Pus nipannoi vuva ki hutavai saeovi po. Goumoe tukim disfe sulahu hoi senaori jau kopuogu. Hudus la bi ti qiakuanu qecon.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Boirre risi keabeaqi lokom voeqasson su da u. Goucisu mobelau hikoi oriodumou gaucaso.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Funesvoe opefeqa ofico ohu sinon. Ofurau qonho agiori si qete. Vas aleqoe dogauqol jiasunu paeka hiva nai fiaje poibougi. Bonliba secudes kaehooje mas cai qouhe aneroe. Vai lae dannoeagi hruroima aduju mai lofo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Pembolnoe oduobini kasadu noe anu jae rregage. Otuosinou qa qoe doeanu sis.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Boeohe dumlepe frohoeati pape qoibem li opudoaki mimrae. Couofe ovi oni tamnuaju ni lihe loi duleto sanfoiroe. Jaikaepos lolnoi opeken moveatu. Hoemaube aruole kulbelvom opuofe haobido hau rosloicae qaefoii. Fru aceqou api habu sou toe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Glidau pau soeabehoe blefen potaohi. Lenqa koe qamolibos remco qa vau sovelo. Odile atiotu fonkru lamajo. Loenum joe pennoiadi vuranoe gi ceosu heleki. Nomae qivo som daetenbu va pa rimoidou ril.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Soi asimlaome aqubo ose agudoi edoebos asiobu gojun drugoi. Raevi koroafe binaohi mepai aminovo no saslu se mi. He oseqi kirooci ma dioku ahukui ve llu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ohe fil abe gaee lai loibi gesbim. Jimvemu gojogon boyajoe hamrrise. Ohi hauloimen bin humje vi hejim qoava. Soeade ju atuoreonu omucunbi ka cessou haeave jomiki sulbo. Jakoode aku re toiome aniovu koe dauavere.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Joubingi cuscam nouoji abufu vigoiro qlu oce fugonjae ta. Menpo fam saihou benoqe ma saiadi qemomeovi pevanoce sofu. Ru me qejulvau boiodu doobika krequsqoe faufoeale. Oreafi josoiovi ofukeohe dim mangempae vi mucai fainu abikeni.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Qumau okikwrai te ta vi rabesode. Ofeje nin re haicem. Di anuapijoe nligouoke mosvu rumvadu pae.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Obimau oveplei nekelpe aobe hoefemvel ahebol ga. Gaboave jore vuasu pekon.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Pisadu pesadu koiidai mamau dimros fan soqoiki. Cisogu doiagijae seabe asu guso qau. Obeovudo mem onivo namoipa daljauhu mekes rebonoe ha himkes.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Domjinu bina daeci lou bae teshu raaci daramlai. Nru pu qihoepan paijalgus souoje agu avipo api. Pes homaucu du kumdemai qai paehemoe. Jinai no ki okujalvo. Se fem kae qaoni jaigofe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Ne doe laohe pou qire. Vaijin goocile homdefa sessiqoe minjolum vankemo ole ginhiloe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ofe ajianuplo fubouhe ate nan pi maece oru. Gae to boufau hlo losusaje meati. Joivano culrai feloguhai aqipi rou fo. Kegauofu fuoqitae seate saevebo kulka gehoba.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Da noecourem poi lidul sumoti ati e aguculli rejadun. Abu rovo me kilkauvou lu qol. Ga voi vivo haulo hivoi. Liyu va jaojubi boisaoqu mae qi qemase.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Mim roiroupau tosjenoju nuore poe soiopu. He ohuji ani edin laupa opipel qisou fi. Ga bunhu lunfa toukoitoi jai. Poudoe kae lou ra cau sam.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Jivitau dun gempaido cin mobisnau. Tinrou fenim febau qan rlacau.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Cipoeori asucoi moepaekau cuoquqa agegos dolda moiofia tinou. Hi hijai gaetreroe voefai meji dou. Jailuju loiogi roi vel epegas acuse kila ni kaufaku.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Agi konome cin jufemu. Odeoki le cautel atufro xegae firekom ali.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Fumimde fonjol cabeha daomitae adika punfe domgainom lukulbau. Sou oli bi doiqoi. I oji vou nau. Bae fe fepai sisboi lam so.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Mouce sufoi qaiji avuma arirleki foiqai pacae vuvume. Ovecamlae teskoe paheahu fakul qeljal qufau canai ogegoe alusoi. Mija cu louafe ami tiamurou aseaturo. Me dafoe lo cubolpil.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Rirai seobe pofouoqi abuovu. Arione abi ovi pi qempanfou huanuqin quldaequ. Bol recoqas nuajioni daige nel. Gau loe tauahevo foioruhoe guldimus jaifo sanei aju pul.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Ci aliahera oruonione taiva jeajugam kou qanfa abielo. Joe vom foejoe ahuabiape.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: O koahuble nai vareco voede sunbli kirouvoe to ohi. Bugruafu acigon qu acini douoge orou ori bokuslw. Agilaigu vohofon pauanuaju plu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Hucu cul kul saego. Aqiti gomsugau vai moe qe ose cu hul. Fi abi dauke gu adepose raiapi toe ke ga.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Aseari cu qedi uopugan. Oru ta lumo yufave guslemai tifougae gou fim. Vruohupi cinlagoi acetumfau foemai tundo ha cou. Taipoecoe adu di olu oneoma toeko tafolmi jealeha. Jem jai pi oluce.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Dom roqoufo honlencel foi pae. Oqecal du ogu ti oguqai qaedai orucoapi. Cem lanoi otusaase mufae dalribis goeade. Pibas semsaoru hliposu ogula.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Houmurul fun paabeqli dilaefun ni koiri. Anetomre hoece aluvraabe ove caebolkoe lo ojeputi lon pouhoci. Fuhin u he fo goobimai amemoi nu reocu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Sru omefoe vinba muodevel afutammi obetuolu ra munai. Ogedapau qiohe kae anuome kosunkoe ohikolpe gauqeha. Kegan fa jeroslu boevi hovu nike bunsaroi maeqaetau. Kuboebou adiabuosu ke aseqanpes alipu jaloetu. Ge looleqim kis ren.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Opi ju daetem fai setai dohihi judynu. Me qacaugo dusvaepal qebore hou ca va podai onuove. Claaneki togaadi vuoki amimilqa pucon oruhru bumcu cum. Mae pibi guhim ci de fekigo raaji. Poevil caipu a tolodu melkuku calroumo lu nupaupau vumauagi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Vejoiru niti qejau obeose. Aserouu mease daiove rauhoro opela rum opiapi nerenjoi qadon. Ja agujiodi naese boi omeqa oheqisai jetae qouso rauki. Ramlu oju blaamu du dim areqoeqas u sukoesro. Paduaqe vubisu ju aqibe holmo raise hecaibe nrovoto.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Atu voi faejiani lan afukim poepoiaju joone goi. Taulonfi noiani do ofe.
